benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: POST /1.0/kb/bundles/{bundleId}/block - Block a bundle

covered: Valid Payload: Successful creation with required and optional fields (TC01–TC04)
Large Payloads: Stress test with large BlockingState payload (TC16)
Input Validation: Malformed body (TC08), missing body (TC10), invalid bundleId format (TC06), invalid requestedDate (TC11), missing/invalid auth (TC09, TC18), injection (TC19), XSS (TC20)
Authorization: Tests for missing/invalid auth tokens (TC09, TC18)
Not Found/Bundle not found scenarios: no bundles (TC05), non-existent bundle (TC07)
Concurrency and Availability: concurrent requests (TC22), network interruption with retry (TC21), service unavailability (TC17), dependent service errors (TC28)
gaps: Rate Limiting / Throttling tests not covered
Caching headers validation for POST responses not covered
recommendations: Add a dedicated duplicate submission test to verify idempotency behavior
Add rate limiting tests to validate 429 responses under high load
Include tests for caching behavior for POST responses if caching is implemented (ETag/Cache-Control) or clarify that POST should not be cached
